Package: orion
Type: Package
Title: Orion - Search Engine for R dataframes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cody Bryant
Maintainer: daftmath@gmail.com
Description: This package will take a seach query as input and score a vector of text items to determine relevancy to the search query.
It uses a vector space model in conjection with term frequency-inverse document frequency and thesaurus/synonym lookup to determine the
relevant items.
License: GPLv3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
  tm,
  magrittr,
  qdap
